 Under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 (``Exchange Act''),
 the Commission is publishing for comment proposed new Rule 3a12-11 and revisions to Rules 12b-7,
 12d1-2,
 and Form 8-A.
 The proposed rule and amendments are intended to provide regulatory relief to issuers listing debt securities on
a national securities exchange. 





