<DOCNO> FR940607-1-00024 </DOCNO>
<PARENT> FR940607-1-00004 </PARENT>
<TEXT>
 

Comment is solicited as to whether it is now desirable for the Commission to adopt rules or exercise definitional authority
under the Exchange Act or Trust Indenture Act to increase the number of issuers with debt securities traded in the OTC
